This is an update of tolua-5.1.4 that adds support 
for string constants.

Example:

  #define NAME "Mikael"

Files modified:

  src/bin/lua/container.lua
  src/bin/lua/define.lua
  src/lib/tolua_map.c
  src/tests/tconstant.h
  src/tests/tconstant.lua
  src/tests/tconstant.pkg
  include/tolua.h

Same terms of use apply to this update as is stated
in the original README file of this distribution:

  tolua is freely available; you can redistribute it and/or modify it.
  The software provided hereunder is on an "as is" basis, and
  the author has no obligation to provide maintenance, support, 
  updates, enhancements, or modifications.

Credit:

  tolua has been designed and implemented by Waldemar Celes,
